Damn!!! That ain't no airplane seat. That's about the size of my house!! I thought he was on the A380 at first, but being that it was on a 777 impressed me even more. Emirates seriously outdid themselves. The fact that you have a TV the size of a TV in a living room and that you can video chat with the flight attendants is AMAZING. That suite is seriously similar to a luxury apartment. Plus, you've got a ton of privacy and you got a fridge right there in your suite. Now Emirates is competing with Etihad. Well done Emirates. Keep it up. And AWESOME video by the way, Casey.
